title: #61 - Harley Morenstein (Epic Meal Time)
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we're joined by the purveyor of the most epic meals known to man- Harley Morenstein! Together we discuss K-Pop fans, nazi dogs, wasting food, and of course ghost stories! Harley Morenstein is the creator of the hugely successful YouTube channel "Epic Meal Time" and a warrior jew.
